    • handle

      public void handle​(org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLOntologyChange change)
      Determines the type of change happening to the ontology and calls the appropriate handle change method.

      If the change is not a know type, then log.info is called.

      Parameters:
      change - is the type of change occuring.
